@startuml activity-routing-decision
!include ../_includes/style.iuml

title Activity — `models.route` decision flow

' Activity diagram for the routing decision logic. Distinct from the
' sequence (which shows WHO calls WHO) — here we show the BRANCHING
' (if embedder, if reliable, if α/β blend, …).

start

:Load `routingConfig`\n+ `effectiveRoutingParams`;
:List eligible candidates\n(D9: complete signature only);
:Probe free memory\n(VRAM/RAM);

if (Embedder configured\n(managed or external)?) then (no)
  :Use R5 deterministic\nclassifier;
  note right
    classifyQuery() returns
    axisWeights from regex /
    keyword analysis.
  end note
  -> r5_path;
else (yes)
  :ensureEmbedderReady()\nOR read external URL;
  if (Embedder live?) then (no)
    :Silent fallback to R5\n(gateReason:'embedder-down');
    -> r5_path;
  else (yes)
    :Measure embedding\nreliability per language\n(fr/zh/en triplets);
    if (All langs ≥ threshold?) then (no)
      :Fallback to R5\n(gateReason:\n'reliability-below-threshold');
      -> r5_path;
    else (yes)
      :Embed query;
      :Project onto 32 leaf anchors;
      if (Per-leaf confidence\nq[i] ≥ θ_q?) then (yes)
        :Descend to LEAF level\n(level:'leaf');
      else (no)
        :Stay at BRANCH level\n(level:'branch');
      endif
      :Blend v = α·v_deterministic\n+ β·max(0, topic_coverage)\n(α=0.7, β=0.3);
      :score_m = Σ q[i]·v_m[i]\n+ w_fit·fit_m + w_hot·hot_m;
      -> vector_done;
    endif
  endif
endif

label r5_path
:axisWeights → branch priors;
:score_m using R5 weights;
label vector_done
:Filter to D9 eligible\nrank by score (desc);
:Build response\n{routedBy, gateReason,\nbest, ranked, resources,\nembeddingReliability?,\nlevel?, axisWeights?};

stop

note right
  routedBy is **always** explicit
  in the response: 'vector' (full
  pipeline) or 'r5' (fallback).
  gateReason explains why for
  each non-vector outcome.
end note

@enduml
